<TITLE> PM appoints new adviser </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, July 9 (bdnews24.com)Prime minister Sheikh Hasina appointed Dr Gauhar Rizvi as a new adviser with cabinet rank on Thursday. The appointment was made under powers vested to the prime minister by the Rules of Business 1996. As the prime minister's adviser, Rizvi will enjoy the salary and facilities of a minister.
